    "description": "〓世界背景〓<br>2042年，一支极地科考队发现了来源未知的巨大类人造物，在对其展开研究的过程中，科研人员发现了人类在过往历史中未曾驾驭过的特殊力量。<br>在特殊的时代背景下，依托于特殊能量实体“无尽之馆”针对超自然事物活动的组织「调查研究控制局（D.I.C.E.）」应运而生。<br>然而，在一个平凡的夜晚，由于前馆长的意外失踪，D.I.C.E.总部爆发了自建立以来最大的失控事态。「你」将作为「馆长候选人」在无尽之馆醒来，临危受命解决此次危机事件。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285600/extras/74d1aad2ae7d545ce65408569059901e.poster.avif?t=1679586935\" width=384 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285600/extras/74d1aad2ae7d545ce65408569059901e.webm?t=1679586935\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285600/extras/74d1aad2ae7d545ce65408569059901e.mp4?t=1679586935\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>〓题材风格〓<br>《未尽行夜》作为一款都市科幻风格的游戏作品，致力于打造冷静克制的风格，而角色表现等也在向具有写实质感的方向努力。我们希望能够打造出一个玩家或多或少都充满一定“熟悉感”的独特都市科幻世界。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285600/extras/422b21572140a31a0c8faa2b73122fc3.poster.avif?t=1679586935\" width=460 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285600/extras/422b21572140a31a0c8faa2b73122fc3.webm?t=1679586935\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285600/extras/422b21572140a31a0c8faa2b73122fc3.mp4?t=1679586935\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>〓动作玩法〓<br>《未尽行夜》是一款重叙事轻策略的3D动作游戏，但在此基础上，《未尽行夜》还加入了逻辑高度和深度的连招与派生机制。玩家所操作的所有角色，都将拥有属于自己特殊的“镜面时间”，当其开启后会获得全新的技能和招式，实现用一个角色打出“两种玩法”。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285600/extras/80f745691b69a63eef04a396cf8c12dd.poster.avif?t=1679586935\" width=384 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285600/extras/80f745691b69a63eef04a396cf8c12dd.webm?t=1679586935\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285600/extras/80f745691b69a63eef04a396cf8c12dd.mp4?t=1679586935\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>不仅如此，《未尽行夜》还在关卡设计上有着重大的革新，在面对各类未知的敌人与异常危机时，玩家可以灵活调整战场的策略，面对不同攻击欲望与性能的敌人采用不同的技能组合；在一些关卡中，玩家还将体验潜行、解谜、防御等特殊玩法。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285600/extras/229f9d7f5a1b6624bcc2279b7ed05cf5.poster.avif?t=1679586935\" width=384 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285600/extras/229f9d7f5a1b6624bcc2279b7ed05cf5.webm?t=1679586935\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285600/extras/229f9d7f5a1b6624bcc2279b7ed05cf5.mp4?t=1679586935\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>长夜未尽，星火将临，欢迎来到鹿湾市。",
